'''Anemones''' were small flowers of many pale colours. [[Frodo Baggins|Frodo]] and [[Samwise Gamgee|Sam]] found white and blue anemones growing in the fragrant flowered lands of [[Ithilien]].<ref>{{TT|IV4}}</ref>  [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]] also hints that [[simbelmynë]] was also a variety of anemone, or at least similar in appearance.

